DESIGN VARIATIONS GENERATOR

CONFIGURATION: n = 3 files

INSTRUCTIONS
Look at the design that has been attached. Create n different versions of that same design. Each version should look different but do the same thing.
Take any additional instructions from the user prompt into account.

FILE MANAGEMENT
Create "variations" folders if not exists
If it exists:
Delete all files in the folder
Find the original design file
Copy it and save as "source.html"
Move "source.html" into "variations" folder
Save all variations under "variations" folder
